{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-05020/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-05020"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["0:50:20"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Creator"]},"value":{"none":["Paul Thomas Anderson"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["plan américain"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["low"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["mobile"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["group shot"]}},{"label":{"none":["Duration"]},"value":{"none":["long take"]}}],"summary":{"none":["A woman places jewelry into an opened purse as woman stand around her."]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05020/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-05020","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05020/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-05020"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05020/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05020/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05020/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05020/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05020/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05020/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05020/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05020/canvas/1/15ce9926-3264-4c44-8e55-2444da41dec8","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-29T19:47:17.937Z","creator":"Tallulah Stallvik","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>According to production designer Mark Tildesley, a “‘space like the <em>Grand Salon </em>for <em>The House of Woodcock </em>had to allow the colors and glory of Reynolds's creations to vibrate and exude wonder. The background had to stand out — but it couldn't interfere with the majesty of <em>Reynolds'</em> designs’” (Burg, “<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW138904967 BCX0\" href=\"https://www.setdecorators.org/?art=film_decor_features&amp;SHOW=SetDecor_Film_Phantom_Thread\"><u>Set Decore</u></a>”).</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05020/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:472.8891248153611,48.72645864106332,597.0088626292466,223.38672451994088"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05020/canvas/1/a1049ead-4925-4a84-a60d-16ba0a0284e4","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-29T19:47:36.569Z","creator":"Tallulah Stallvik","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Though Alma is ostensibly the lowest ranking in terms of status among the women in the room, she is foregrounded as the tallest and most imposing figure. This hieratic composition—an artistic technique in which the most important figure is denoted by their large scale—suggests that Alma will ultimately become the center of power.</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05020/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:231.01550960118084,74.16497415066446,222.54200516986702,898.5390509601181"}}}]}]}]}